  "texts": [
    "The next step was to customise the chatbot using the fine-tuned model in which the AI assistant embodies a given political party's view expressed on social media.",
    "Drawing from the Q&A preset from OpenAI, we input as a prompt a short bot's identity description coupled with an example of answer / questions for each politician: Source: https://github.com/musielena.",
    "After having checked the soundness of the completions in the playground, we then used OpenAI's API to generate GPT-3 responses in Python.",
    "This allowed us to implement a chat.",
    "log function to ensure that the bot would remember the dialogue history."
  ]
}